      "writtenOn": "2015-09-28T18:16:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is a Qemu1-specific implementation of SerialLine interface which wraps the CharDriverState interface. It feels to me like CharSerialLine is good name for it, and if we put it in the qemu1 glue code then Qemu prefix won\u0027t really be needed.\nAlso, if there\u0027s any other implementation in qemu1, the QemuSerialLine name would become too generic",
