      "writtenOn": "2015-09-28T07:59:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Interesting, is there any reason why read() and canRead() cannot be virtual abstract methods of the interface? I\u0027m thinking that in the future, we will want a mock implementation that will be used to unit-test qemud, so the simpler the better.",
      "revId": "6e91c884e0d90e27bbd7ae44c0878e0201f5b6d5",
