      "writtenOn": "2015-09-29T15:55:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ok, let\u0027s not sweat it then. I think it\u0027s possible to do both, but I\u0027m much more interested in having a working AndroidEmu right now, so let\u0027s allow it :) Thanks for the clarification.",
